      "comment": "CHIVAS LADY (2) has been a little hard to follow, finishing out of the placings latest but was in winning form two back scoring in a TG1-4W at this track. Has the ability and looks a key chance here. CADILLAC EXPRESS (4) is rarely out of the finish, recording six places from 11 starts. Has finished in the placings two on end now, the latest when third (18.07) at this track. Hard to beat again. COMPTON BOWIE (1) turned in a plain effort last time when seventh at this track over 400m behind Dirty Dash (23.99) in a Grade 4/5. Goes well out of this box with a win and four minor placings. Can do much better this time. MOONLIGHT NELLIE (8) can run a bold race on best form.",
